<text id="02-output-contract" title="Testing (Multi-Language) — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying testing. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['aaa_pattern', 'tests_isolated', 'tests_idempotent', 'coverage_gate_present', 'lanes_separated'],
  "properties": {
    "aaa_pattern": { "type": "boolean" },
    "tests_isolated": { "type": "boolean" },
    "tests_idempotent": { "type": "boolean" },
    "coverage_gate_present": { "type": "boolean" },
    "lanes_separated": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>aaa_pattern</item>
      <item>tests_isolated</item>
      <item>tests_idempotent</item>
      <item>coverage_gate_present</item>
      <item>lanes_separated</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "aaa_pattern": true,
  "tests_isolated": true,
  "tests_idempotent": true,
  "coverage_gate_present": true,
  "lanes_separated": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "aaa_pattern": false,
  "tests_isolated": false,
  "tests_idempotent": false,
  "coverage_gate_present": false,
  "lanes_separated": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-aaa-pattern).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
